# Dev/runtime artifacts for the terminal-CLI hook capture — these belong in the
# developer's workspace, never in the shipped extension. activity.jsonl holds
# captured session data (paths, commands, tool I/O); settings.local.json holds
# local permissions. The watcher's runtime code is bundled into dist/.
.claude/**
.codecubicle/**
